description: “One of the greatest discoveries a person makes one of their great surprises is to find they can do what they were afraid they couldn't do.” “If everyone is moving forward together then success takes care of itself.” “Experience is the thing of supreme value.”
The BMW slogan “Sheer Driving Pleasure” has evolved over the years from various brand claims in German. The term “pleasure” first appeared in the 1930s in BMW ads.
